nonceRequired="false" means that an error will be thrown if a 'nonce security header' is supplied.
nonceRequired="true" means that an error will be thrown if a 'nonce security header' is NOT supplied.
see com.sun.xml.wss.impl.filter.AuthenticationTokenFilter [library code]

